Its the first zombie survival map ive done, i spent really long time on it but really much got away when i was doing other stuff att the same time so i cant check total time in the source sdk use time.

it contains:
* A abandomed pre-barricated house
* Flicking lights
* Jail looking thing
* Dark (and light) areas
* Small rooms to barricade in
* Objects in almost every room
* Elevators
* Fires
 And more.   

thats pretty much everything that pops up ion my head atm
